            "body": "<p>Well, this might be not a correct answer to your actual question but maybe it helps somehow.  If you have the possibility you might want to consider using the JodaTime library <a href=\"http://www.joda.org/joda-time/\" rel=\"nofollow\">JodaTime<\/a>\nwich has much mor convenient methods for doing such things. For instance just adding a month to any given date, or get the maximum number of days for a given month.<\/p>\n",
